about teaching quantum physics

00:35:50.610 --> 00:35:54.400 align:middle line:84%
to people who are not scientists
at all is that it provides

00:35:54.400 --> 00:35:57.610 align:middle line:84%
a much stronger
metaphorical base,

00:35:57.610 --> 00:36:01.640 align:middle line:84%
a language structure in
which we can renegotiate

00:36:01.640 --> 00:36:06.170 align:middle line:84%
our relationships with others,
that we can learn that it's OK

00:36:06.170 --> 00:36:09.780 align:middle line:84%
to give up the old thinking
and look at some new ways

00:36:09.780 --> 00:36:15.400 align:middle line:84%
of thinking to help us deal with
the problems that we're going

00:36:15.400 --> 00:36:19.440 align:middle line:84%
to be facing as
we face 7 billion,

00:36:19.440 --> 00:36:25.580 align:middle line:84%
maybe more people on the planet
learning how to re-resource,

00:36:25.580 --> 00:36:26.580 align:middle line:90%
learning how to--

00:36:26.580 --> 00:36:27.205 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Energy.

00:36:27.205 --> 00:36:29.350 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: --re-change
our concept of what

00:36:29.350 --> 00:36:32.850 align:middle line:84%
is-- why we have to kill each
other rather than maybe there's

00:36:32.850 --> 00:36:33.350 align:middle line:90%
another way.

00:36:33.350 --> 00:36:35.510 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: It's interesting,
because if we could just

00:36:35.510 --> 00:36:38.440 align:middle line:84%
get our global leaders to think
more like this, because they're

00:36:38.440 --> 00:36:41.800 align:middle line:84%
so ingrained in either
the monetary structures

00:36:41.800 --> 00:36:45.340 align:middle line:90%
around energy and oil and gas.

00:36:45.340 --> 00:36:46.880 align:middle line:90%


00:36:46.880 --> 00:36:47.840 align:middle line:90%
Greed gets involved.

00:36:47.840 --> 00:36:51.530 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: It's the old way
based upon survival, based

00:36:51.530 --> 00:36:54.870 align:middle line:84%
upon that we have to have these
things in order to survive,

00:36:54.870 --> 00:36:56.970 align:middle line:84%
and if we cut those
things off, we

00:36:56.970 --> 00:37:00.505 align:middle line:84%
won't be able to survive
like we're used to surviving.

00:37:00.505 --> 00:37:02.155 align:middle line:90%


00:37:02.155 --> 00:37:04.940 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Do you think that
will happen in our lifetime?

00:37:04.940 --> 00:37:06.805 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: I think
it's happening now.

00:37:06.805 --> 00:37:07.930 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: In certain pockets.

00:37:07.930 --> 00:37:09.915 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: And it's going
to continue to happen.

00:37:09.915 --> 00:37:11.020 align:middle line:90%


00:37:11.020 --> 00:37:15.380 align:middle line:84%
Enlightenment is a process
which will continue,

00:37:15.380 --> 00:37:18.750 align:middle line:84%
and I'm part of that process,
and the other teachers

00:37:18.750 --> 00:37:21.270 align:middle line:84%
that you've had on this program
are part of that process,

00:37:21.270 --> 00:37:25.100 align:middle line:84%
and we're continuing to keep
getting the message out.

00:37:25.100 --> 00:37:29.930 align:middle line:84%
And I think it's important
that Gaiam TV helps

00:37:29.930 --> 00:37:33.680 align:middle line:84%
producing such
information for people

00:37:33.680 --> 00:37:35.380 align:middle line:90%
other than the usual thing.

