scene in order

00:37:42.900 --> 00:37:46.270 align:middle line:84%
to let them know that there
are other ways to do it,

00:37:46.270 --> 00:37:49.910 align:middle line:84%
and as the bottom line
suitors would say,

00:37:49.910 --> 00:37:51.730 align:middle line:84%
there's money to
made here, guys.

00:37:51.730 --> 00:37:53.230 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: It's always
the bottom line.

00:37:53.230 --> 00:37:56.630 align:middle line:84%
But that was the Global
Alliance of Transformational

00:37:56.630 --> 00:37:58.220 align:middle line:84%
Entertainment,
and that is what--

00:37:58.220 --> 00:38:00.570 align:middle line:84%
there's a lot of different
sectors like that where there

00:38:00.570 --> 00:38:02.910 align:middle line:84%
are transformational
movements, but this

00:38:02.910 --> 00:38:05.790 align:middle line:84%
has existed since
the '60s, the '70s.

00:38:05.790 --> 00:38:08.200 align:middle line:84%
I mean, people have
constantly been

00:38:08.200 --> 00:38:11.200 align:middle line:84%
trying to achieve this
level of enlightenment.

00:38:11.200 --> 00:38:13.960 align:middle line:84%
It's in different genres
in different ways.

00:38:13.960 --> 00:38:16.500 align:middle line:90%
Are we getting more evolved?

00:38:16.500 --> 00:38:18.025 align:middle line:84%
Are we getting any
closer, or are we

00:38:18.025 --> 00:38:19.950 align:middle line:84%
just recreating the same
story over and over?

00:38:19.950 --> 00:38:20.890 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: Well,
there's always going

00:38:20.890 --> 00:38:22.880 align:middle line:84%
to be re-creation
over and over again.

00:38:22.880 --> 00:38:24.860 align:middle line:84%
There are always going
to be pockets of that.

00:38:24.860 --> 00:38:26.660 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: As we've just
learned through that concept.

00:38:26.660 --> 00:38:27.909 align:middle line:90%
>>WOLF: It's the way it works.

00:38:27.909 --> 00:38:32.110 align:middle line:84%
I mean, once we've learned
something that we've-- once

00:38:32.110 --> 00:38:35.890 align:middle line:84%
you've learned that
if I'm an Israeli,

00:38:35.890 --> 00:38:39.860 align:middle line:84%
