that live in that country,

00:38:39.860 --> 00:38:42.640 align:middle line:84%
or if I live in that country,
I may not like the Israelis.

00:38:42.640 --> 00:38:45.340 align:middle line:84%
If I'm an Iranian, I'm
worried about-- if we

00:38:45.340 --> 00:38:50.210 align:middle line:84%
have certain ways of
thinking going on our head,

00:38:50.210 --> 00:38:54.050 align:middle line:84%
we may tend to see the
world as the enemy.

00:38:54.050 --> 00:38:58.260 align:middle line:84%
But there are also
transformations going on.

00:38:58.260 --> 00:39:01.060 align:middle line:90%
The web has made that possible.

00:39:01.060 --> 00:39:04.820 align:middle line:84%
No longer is war hidden
from us, and once people

00:39:04.820 --> 00:39:05.779 align:middle line:90%
see the horror of war--

00:39:05.779 --> 00:39:06.653 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: This is true.

00:39:06.653 --> 00:39:08.750 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: --like what's going
on in Syria right now,

00:39:08.750 --> 00:39:10.520 align:middle line:84%
transformation
starts to take place.

00:39:10.520 --> 00:39:11.855 align:middle line:90%
It's going on a lot faster.

00:39:11.855 --> 00:39:13.855 align:middle line:84%
People don't think it's
fast because they seldom

00:39:13.855 --> 00:39:17.190 align:middle line:84%
see the horrors of Syria,
but it's much faster now

00:39:17.190 --> 00:39:19.529 align:middle line:84%
that people are taking
pictures on cell phones.

00:39:19.529 --> 00:39:20.070 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yeah.

00:39:20.070 --> 00:39:22.830 align:middle line:84%
Time does appear to be speeding
up because of the internet,

00:39:22.830 --> 00:39:25.740 align:middle line:84%
and there are less things
that are covered up

00:39:25.740 --> 00:39:27.984 align:middle line:84%
now because of the
exposure on the internet.

00:39:27.984 --> 00:39:29.400 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: Can't cover
it up anymore.

00:39:29.400 --> 00:39:31.430 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Sometimes there's
too much information,

00:39:31.430 --> 00:39:33.304 align:middle line:84%
so you don't know what
to believe any longer,

00:39:33.304 --> 00:39:36.377 align:middle line:84%
but it is up to-- that's why
I'm all about empowering people

00:39:36.377 --> 00:39:38.418 align:middle line:84%
to find their own truth
in it because you know it

00:39:38.418 --> 00:39:39.860 align:middle line:90%
when you hit it.

00:39:39.860 --> 00:39:40.360 align:middle line:90%
All right.

