So we're going to continue our
conversation on how this all

00:39:43.620 --> 00:39:45.160 align:middle line:90%
relates to us on a global scale.

00:39:45.160 --> 00:39:47.270 align:middle line:84%
And I want people to
understand this is, again,

00:39:47.270 --> 00:39:48.160 align:middle line:90%
the macro and micro.

00:39:48.160 --> 00:39:52.850 align:middle line:84%
We're looking at our individual
stages of development as people

00:39:52.850 --> 00:39:54.975 align:middle line:84%
and where we go through
our adolescence, adulthood,

00:39:54.975 --> 00:39:56.380 align:middle line:90%
and where we go into our life.

00:39:56.380 --> 00:39:58.280 align:middle line:84%
We're looking at the
global perspective

00:39:58.280 --> 00:40:02.040 align:middle line:84%
on how we are as an evolution
and our society evolves

00:40:02.040 --> 00:40:02.950 align:middle line:90%
and so forth.

00:40:02.950 --> 00:40:05.000 align:middle line:84%
And we're looking at this
in terms of the future

00:40:05.000 --> 00:40:07.130 align:middle line:84%
as well because this
absolutely impacts our future.

00:40:07.130 --> 00:40:10.280 align:middle line:84%
I want to always make sure what
you're talking about applies

00:40:10.280 --> 00:40:12.980 align:middle line:84%
to reality because we
could get way out there

00:40:12.980 --> 00:40:15.450 align:middle line:84%
in our conversations
in a very esoteric way.

00:40:15.450 --> 00:40:16.615 align:middle line:90%
But I absolutely love it.

00:40:16.615 --> 00:40:16.798 align:middle line:90%
>>WOLF: Who me?

