Never.

00:40:19.380 --> 00:40:21.452 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Dr. Quantum.

00:40:21.452 --> 00:40:24.400 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: Dr. Quantum
is always here.

00:40:24.400 --> 00:40:27.590 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Well, it's great though
because you think like this,

00:40:27.590 --> 00:40:29.260 align:middle line:84%
and you also bring
it back into reality.

00:40:29.260 --> 00:40:30.030 align:middle line:90%
>>WOLF: I hope so.

00:40:30.030 --> 00:40:30.680 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: I absolutely
