Welcome back.

00:40:41.400 --> 00:40:44.570 align:middle line:84%
My guest is quantum physicist
Fred Alan Wolf, otherwise known

00:40:44.570 --> 00:40:45.890 align:middle line:90%
as Dr. Quantum.

00:40:45.890 --> 00:40:49.240 align:middle line:84%
We're talking about the field--
the idea of time speeding up,

00:40:49.240 --> 00:40:52.360 align:middle line:84%
the quantum field theory,
time moving faster than light.

00:40:52.360 --> 00:40:54.720 align:middle line:84%
So we're going to get on to
the meaty stuff right now.

00:40:54.720 --> 00:40:56.480 align:middle line:90%
So let's talk about that.

00:40:56.480 --> 00:40:57.980 align:middle line:90%
What is matter, really?

00:40:57.980 --> 00:41:00.575 align:middle line:90%
>>WOLF: Well, in the beginning--

00:41:00.575 --> 00:41:01.612 align:middle line:90%


00:41:01.612 --> 00:41:02.940 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: You were there?

00:41:02.940 --> 00:41:03.440 align:middle line:90%
>>WOLF: Yes.

00:41:03.440 --> 00:41:05.600 align:middle line:90%
We were all there.

00:41:05.600 --> 00:41:09.300 align:middle line:84%
In the beginning, there wasn't
matter, there wasn't space,

00:41:09.300 --> 00:41:11.170 align:middle line:90%
there wasn't time.

00:41:11.170 --> 00:41:11.860 align:middle line:90%
What was there?

00:41:11.860 --> 00:41:14.590 align:middle line:90%
Well, that's kind of a mystery.

00:41:14.590 --> 00:41:20.350 align:middle line:84%
But suddenly there was something
called the big-- the Big Bang.

00:41:20.350 --> 00:41:24.760 align:middle line:84%
And then matter, space, and
time all came into existence

00:41:24.760 --> 00:41:26.420 align:middle line:90%
supposedly at once.

00:41:26.420 --> 00:41:30.250 align:middle line:84%
And so what we've
learned from physics

00:41:30.250 --> 00:41:33.800 align:middle line:84%
is that you can't have any
of those without the other.

00:41:33.800 --> 00:41:35.150 align:middle line:90%


00:41:35.150 --> 00:41:37.405 align:middle line:84%
Can't have time without
space and matter.

00:41:37.405 --> 00:41:39.590 align:middle line:84%
Can't have matter
without time and space.

00:41:39.590 --> 00:41:41.540 align:middle line:84%
Can't have space
without time and matter.

00:41:41.540 --> 00:41:47.370 align:middle line:84%
They are a twining,
triplicate twining, a braid.

00:41:47.370 --> 00:41:50.865 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: You, though, then bring
God into this whole thing,

00:41:50.865 --> 00:41:51.365 align:middle line:90%
which is--

00:41:51.365 --> 00:41:52.920 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: Well, that
was before this

00:41:52.920 --> 00:41:55.915 align:middle line:84%
all kind of big
banged into existence.

00:41:55.915 --> 00:41:57.640 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: But you do yourself.

00:41:57.640 --> 00:42:00.230 align:middle line:84%
You're a quantum physicist
that brings together

00:42:00.230 --> 00:42:03.315 align:middle line:84%
spirituality and
science and physics.

00:42:03.315 --> 00:42:06.090 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: Well, in a way this
is kind of like a story

00:42:06.090 --> 00:42:08.740 align:middle line:84%
because, you see,
in the ancient days,

00:42:08.740 --> 00:42:13.000 align:middle line:84%
there used to be a guy
called Arjuna who was a king.

00:42:13.000 --> 00:42:16.440 align:middle line:84%
And he wanted to know about
these kinds of questions.

00:42:16.440 --> 00:42:17.510 align:middle line:90%
Why am I here?

00:42:17.510 --> 00:42:22.110 align:middle line:84%
Why is life-- he had to go into
a battle, and in that battle

00:42:22.110 --> 00:42:26.020 align:middle line:84%
there were people on the other
side, the so-called enemy,

00:42:26.020 --> 00:42:28.600 align:middle line:84%
which included relatives
of his and so forth.

00:42:28.600 --> 00:42:30.540 align:middle line:84%
And he didn't want to
kill all those guys.

00:42:30.540 --> 00:42:35.860 align:middle line:84%
And so he had a driver
who drove him around

00:42:35.860 --> 00:42:40.650 align:middle line:90%
in his cart, his chariot.

00:42:40.650 --> 00:42:44.680 align:middle line:84%
And one day he walked out
into the-- those of you

00:42:44.680 --> 00:42:48.070 align:middle line:84%
that know the Hindu scriptures
and know the Bhagavad Gita

00:42:48.070 --> 00:42:49.880 align:middle line:84%
are going to probably
really hate my story.

00:42:49.880 --> 00:42:51.652 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: You're
butchering it right now.

00:42:51.652 --> 00:42:53.735 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: I'm telling it my
way, but nevertheless, I

00:42:53.735 --> 00:42:55.460 align:middle line:84%
think my way is
kind of fun anyway.

00:42:55.460 --> 00:42:59.730 align:middle line:84%
So anyway, Arjuna goes
walking out into the field,

00:42:59.730 --> 00:43:05.250 align:middle line:84%
and there are all the
charioteer-- drivers

00:43:05.250 --> 00:43:08.719 align:middle line:84%
are all sitting around their
fields having a marijuana

00:43:08.719 --> 00:43:10.260 align:middle line:84%
cigarette or something,
whatever they

00:43:10.260 --> 00:43:11.856 align:middle line:90%
were smoking in those days.

00:43:11.856 --> 00:43:15.060 align:middle line:84%
Who knows what they were
smoking or drinking-- something.

00:43:15.060 --> 00:43:15.630 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: And?

00:43:15.630 --> 00:43:20.120 align:middle line:84%
And so-called here
comes Arjuna up

00:43:20.120 --> 00:43:23.250 align:middle line:84%
to his driver who happens
to have the name Krishna.

00:43:23.250 --> 00:43:24.100 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:43:24.100 --> 00:43:24.913 align:middle line:90%


00:43:24.913 --> 00:43:25.704 align:middle line:90%
We've heard of him.

00:43:25.704 --> 00:43:27.370 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: Now that may
strike you as being

00:43:27.370 --> 00:43:30.320 align:middle line:84%
strange because Krishna is the
god of-- you know, the big god.

00:43:30.320 --> 00:43:35.120 align:middle line:84%
But actually, I've driven around
in cabs in New York many times,

00:43:35.120 --> 00:43:37.030 align:middle line:84%
and I've been
driven by Mohammad.

00:43:37.030 --> 00:43:40.070 align:middle line:84%
I've been driven
by Jesus, Moses.

00:43:40.070 --> 00:43:40.982 align:middle line:90%
You know?

00:43:40.982 --> 00:43:42.350 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Krishna.

00:43:42.350 --> 00:43:43.262 align:middle line:90%
>>WOLF: Krishna.

00:43:43.262 --> 00:43:44.085 align:middle line:90%


00:43:44.085 --> 00:43:45.460 align:middle line:84%
So it's not so
surprising that he

00:43:45.460 --> 00:43:47.456 align:middle line:84%
would have a driver
named Krishna.

00:43:47.456 --> 00:43:50.212 align:middle line:84%
So he says to Krishna,
he says, OK, you know,

00:43:50.212 --> 00:43:52.003 align:middle line:84%
I'm worried about this
battle and so forth.

00:43:52.003 --> 00:43:53.290 align:middle line:84%
Krisna says don't
worry about a thing.

00:43:53.290 --> 00:43:54.500 align:middle line:90%
I've got it all covered.

00:43:54.500 --> 00:43:55.583 align:middle line:90%
He says, what do you mean?

00:43:55.583 --> 00:43:58.170 align:middle line:84%
He says because I'm not just
Krishna, your ordinary driver,

00:43:58.170 --> 00:43:59.702 align:middle line:90%
I'm the big Krishna.

00:43:59.702 --> 00:44:01.910 align:middle line:84%
And he says, what do you
mean you're the big Krishna?

00:44:01.910 --> 00:44:03.000 align:middle line:90%
He says, I'll show you.

00:44:03.000 --> 00:44:06.850 align:middle line:84%
And suddenly Krishna
reveals his true being.

00:44:06.850 --> 00:44:10.900 align:middle line:84%
And his true being is
like an infinity of suns.

00:44:10.900 --> 00:44:17.010 align:middle line:84%
And suddenly, Arjuna,
looking at all of the beings,

00:44:17.010 --> 00:44:23.060 align:middle line:84%
all of the faces, all the
physiognomies of Krishna,

00:44:23.060 --> 00:44:27.830 align:middle line:84%
suddenly sees in that list of
all those faces, his own face.

00:44:27.830 --> 00:44:29.330 align:middle line:90%


00:44:29.330 --> 00:44:36.530 align:middle line:84%
And then he realizes Arjuna is
Krishna, and Krishna is Arjuna.

00:44:36.530 --> 00:44:39.640 align:middle line:90%
But this has been all time.

00:44:39.640 --> 00:44:41.630 align:middle line:90%
Krishna is showing him all time.

00:44:41.630 --> 00:44:47.720 align:middle line:84%
In fact he's saying, I am
time itself, and you are me.

00:44:47.720 --> 00:44:50.440 align:middle line:84%
So this is the first
revelation about the nature

00:44:50.440 --> 00:44:51.685 align:middle line:90%
of time and space.

00:44:51.685 --> 00:44:54.037 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: So I could be you.

00:44:54.037 --> 00:44:55.910 align:middle line:84%
You could be me right
now in this quantum

00:44:55.910 --> 00:44:56.610 align:middle line:90%
field of entanglement.

00:44:56.610 --> 00:44:57.150 align:middle line:90%
>>WOLF: Exactly.

00:44:57.150 --> 00:44:59.525 align:middle line:84%
And that's really what the
quantum entanglement is really

00:44:59.525 --> 00:45:06.160 align:middle line:84%
telling us is that we are
timeless in this very anciently

