ordinary matter.

00:51:35.270 --> 00:51:37.690 align:middle line:84%
In fact, one of the
big hints that we've

00:51:37.690 --> 00:51:39.520 align:middle line:84%
learned from quantum
physics and a thing

00:51:39.520 --> 00:51:42.410 align:middle line:84%
called quantum field
theory is that matter

00:51:42.410 --> 00:51:46.330 align:middle line:84%
has to play the game
of causality, which

00:51:46.330 --> 00:51:50.850 align:middle line:84%
means that cause and effect have
to be related in such a way.

00:51:50.850 --> 00:51:53.980 align:middle line:84%
And the only way they can
be related in such a way

00:51:53.980 --> 00:51:57.670 align:middle line:84%
as we call causality, that
something happens first

00:51:57.670 --> 00:51:59.990 align:middle line:84%
and then something
happens as a result

00:51:59.990 --> 00:52:03.280 align:middle line:84%
