beginning and end.

00:52:03.280 --> 00:52:08.930 align:middle line:84%
In order for that
to happen, you must

00:52:08.930 --> 00:52:12.110 align:middle line:84%
have a way in which
whatever happened

00:52:12.110 --> 00:52:17.140 align:middle line:84%
first can send
information to what

00:52:17.140 --> 00:52:23.760 align:middle line:84%
