00:58:18.040 --> 00:58:19.070 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: I understand.

00:58:19.070 --> 00:58:20.278 align:middle line:90%
>>WOLF: --within the nucleus.

00:58:20.278 --> 00:58:20.778 align:middle line:90%


