>>WOLF: Stay tuned.

00:59:18.701 --> 00:59:21.250 align:middle line:84%
So now let's get into this
God's mind, this matrix

00:59:21.250 --> 00:59:23.830 align:middle line:84%
of hidden field where God
said, let there be light,

00:59:23.830 --> 00:59:24.980 align:middle line:90%
and there was light.

00:59:24.980 --> 00:59:27.763 align:middle line:84%
As I say, in Hebrew it's vayomer
Elohim yehi-or vayehi-or.

00:59:27.763 --> 00:59:31.090 align:middle line:90%


