>>WOLF: Exactly.

01:07:34.090 --> 01:07:34.600 align:middle line:90%
Exactly.

01:07:34.600 --> 01:07:37.100 align:middle line:84%
So now, we've got
some idea about how

01:07:37.100 --> 01:07:38.250 align:middle line:90%
