produces the material

01:17:30.370 --> 01:17:31.695 align:middle line:90%
world of matter.

01:17:31.695 --> 01:17:32.980 align:middle line:90%


01:17:32.980 --> 01:17:37.826 align:middle line:84%
Through time reflections,
it produces a mental world

01:17:37.826 --> 01:17:38.325 align:middle line:90%
of mind.

01:17:38.325 --> 01:17:39.456 align:middle line:90%


01:17:39.456 --> 01:17:41.920 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So in the very
beginning of the show

01:17:41.920 --> 01:17:45.900 align:middle line:84%
when I talked about how we're
going to look at time, space,

01:17:45.900 --> 01:17:49.030 align:middle line:84%
