very, very different.

01:17:58.815 --> 01:18:03.820 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: They're different
but they're essentially

01:18:03.820 --> 01:18:09.940 align:middle line:84%
we're looking at how the mind
of God is working by producing

01:18:09.940 --> 01:18:13.230 align:middle line:84%
