01:18:16.610 --> 01:18:18.340 align:middle line:84%
Now, there's a
second kind of light

01:18:18.340 --> 01:18:20.380 align:middle line:84%
which I haven't
talked about yet,

01:18:20.380 --> 01:18:23.160 align:middle line:84%
and that's the light that
we see with our eyes,

01:18:23.160 --> 01:18:24.710 align:middle line:90%
