one place to another.

01:18:42.550 --> 01:18:45.310 align:middle line:84%
The spin 1/2 half
stuff is structuring,

01:18:45.310 --> 01:18:46.350 align:middle line:90%
getting things in order.

01:18:46.350 --> 01:18:48.250 align:middle line:90%


01:18:48.250 --> 01:18:52.750 align:middle line:84%
The spin-1 stuff is sending
things through space and time,

01:18:52.750 --> 01:18:55.477 align:middle line:84%
and that's what light does,
the ordinary light we see.

01:18:55.477 --> 01:18:57.810 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So really, basically,
what we're looking at here

01:18:57.810 --> 01:19:00.340 align:middle line:90%
