This interview is an illusion
if you think about it.

01:19:11.320 --> 01:19:13.590 align:middle line:84%
So if everything is
truly an illusion--

01:19:13.590 --> 01:19:15.290 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: Everything
is, in a sense,

01:19:15.290 --> 01:19:20.230 align:middle line:84%
