01:19:36.067 --> 01:19:36.650 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Right.

01:19:36.650 --> 01:19:38.300 align:middle line:84%
So we're the observer
and the performer

01:19:38.300 --> 01:19:39.246 align:middle line:84%
and the observer
and the performer.

01:19:39.246 --> 01:19:40.121 align:middle line:90%
>>WOLF: That's right.

01:19:40.121 --> 01:19:42.120 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So then how this
applies to our lives

