that same illusion.

01:20:01.020 --> 01:20:02.850 align:middle line:84%
So we can go forward
and to create

01:20:02.850 --> 01:20:08.080 align:middle line:84%
into new ways of thinking, of
new sources of free energy,

01:20:08.080 --> 01:20:10.770 align:middle line:84%
of new ways of
forming government,

01:20:10.770 --> 01:20:12.567 align:middle line:84%
of new ways of
forming relationships.

