You could bring it down
to the mundane level

01:20:14.400 --> 01:20:17.050 align:middle line:84%
of new ways of
creating your health,

01:20:17.050 --> 01:20:19.324 align:middle line:84%
and this is how this
all comes together.

01:20:19.324 --> 01:20:19.990 align:middle line:90%
>>WOLF: Exactly.

01:20:19.990 --> 01:20:21.120 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

