>>LISA: Acting as if, yes.

01:21:37.040 --> 01:21:40.940 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: Acting as if, you
know, and that's fine.

01:21:40.940 --> 01:21:44.120 align:middle line:84%
Thinking how you were in the
past, that's also a fantasy,

01:21:44.120 --> 01:21:45.450 align:middle line:90%
