01:22:14.150 --> 01:22:16.230 align:middle line:90%
in the law of attraction.

01:22:16.230 --> 01:22:20.109 align:middle line:84%
I couldn't quite put my fingers
on it and say it's a law.

01:22:20.109 --> 01:22:21.900 align:middle line:84%
It's certainly not a
law of physics the way

01:22:21.900 --> 01:22:23.500 align:middle line:90%
it was being presented, no.

01:22:23.500 --> 01:22:27.510 align:middle line:84%
It's really more of
a metaphor for stuff.

01:22:27.510 --> 01:22:29.850 align:middle line:90%


01:22:29.850 --> 01:22:32.650 align:middle line:84%
To teach people that
all you gotta do

01:22:32.650 --> 01:22:37.360 align:middle line:84%
is wish for winning
the lotto and you're

01:22:37.360 --> 01:22:38.840 align:middle line:90%
going to win the lottery.

01:22:38.840 --> 01:22:42.324 align:middle line:84%
Well, what I do to
people, I say, OK.

01:22:42.324 --> 01:22:43.740 align:middle line:84%
That's going to
work, but you also

01:22:43.740 --> 01:22:48.400 align:middle line:84%
have to consider that everybody
wants the same thing you want.

01:22:48.400 --> 01:22:50.730 align:middle line:84%
So let everybody go out
and buy a separate lotto

01:22:50.730 --> 01:22:53.280 align:middle line:84%
ticket and everybody
wants to win the lotto.

01:22:53.280 --> 01:22:55.615 align:middle line:84%
And let's say that you
all buy the same lotto

01:22:55.615 --> 01:22:58.320 align:middle line:84%
ticket, the same winning
numbers, and you all win.

01:22:58.320 --> 01:23:00.200 align:middle line:90%
How much money do you get?

01:23:00.200 --> 01:23:04.780 align:middle line:84%
Actually you'll get, on a $5
ticket, you may get $0.03.

01:23:04.780 --> 01:23:08.355 align:middle line:84%
So you won the lotto, but
it wasn't worth it, was it?

01:23:08.355 --> 01:23:10.780 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: But does the law
that like attracts like

01:23:10.780 --> 01:23:12.680 align:middle line:84%
apply to the law of
attraction at all?

01:23:12.680 --> 01:23:13.916 align:middle line:90%
>>WOLF: Not really.

01:23:13.916 --> 01:23:18.011 align:middle line:84%
It's really like attracts
unlike in the physical, material

01:23:18.011 --> 01:23:18.510 align:middle line:90%
world.

01:23:18.510 --> 01:23:21.036 align:middle line:84%
That's what we talk-- remember
we were talking about charge

01:23:21.036 --> 01:23:22.160 align:middle line:90%
and matter and anti-matter.

01:23:22.160 --> 01:23:23.750 align:middle line:90%


01:23:23.750 --> 01:23:26.130 align:middle line:84%
Positrons and electrons
are matter and anti-matter,

01:23:26.130 --> 01:23:29.112 align:middle line:84%
and they will attract each
other and annihilate each other.

01:23:29.112 --> 01:23:29.945 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Interesting.

01:23:29.945 --> 01:23:32.000 align:middle line:90%
>>WOLF: So like attracts unlike.

01:23:32.000 --> 01:23:35.800 align:middle line:90%


01:23:35.800 --> 01:23:38.910 align:middle line:84%
You know, the whole idea
of using the idea like

01:23:38.910 --> 01:23:41.070 align:middle line:84%
attracts like, it's a
kind of a mixed metaphor.

01:23:41.070 --> 01:23:42.970 align:middle line:90%


01:23:42.970 --> 01:23:45.300 align:middle line:84%
It really doesn't
quite work that way.

01:23:45.300 --> 01:23:48.661 align:middle line:84%
So I never used that in the
film when I was in the movie.

01:23:48.661 --> 01:23:49.702 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: "What the Bleep?"

01:23:49.702 --> 01:23:50.230 align:middle line:90%
>>WOLF: No.

01:23:50.230 --> 01:23:50.860 align:middle line:90%
No.

01:23:50.860 --> 01:23:52.485 align:middle line:90%
In the movie "The Secret."

01:23:52.485 --> 01:23:53.450 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

01:23:53.450 --> 01:23:57.340 align:middle line:84%
So when you have an idea
of like attract like,

01:23:57.340 --> 01:23:58.996 align:middle line:90%
like attracts unlike.

01:23:58.996 --> 01:23:59.620 align:middle line:90%
>>WOLF: Unlike.

01:23:59.620 --> 01:24:01.230 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: How do you
apply that to like?

01:24:01.230 --> 01:24:03.250 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: Well, you have
to think about that.

01:24:03.250 --> 01:24:05.900 align:middle line:90%


01:24:05.900 --> 01:24:09.660 align:middle line:84%
If you-- Here you
are a superstar.

01:24:09.660 --> 01:24:11.860 align:middle line:90%


01:24:11.860 --> 01:24:13.230 align:middle line:90%
Walk down the street, superstar.

01:24:13.230 --> 01:24:14.510 align:middle line:90%


01:24:14.510 --> 01:24:15.375 align:middle line:90%
See who you attract.

01:24:15.375 --> 01:24:17.990 align:middle line:90%


01:24:17.990 --> 01:24:19.677 align:middle line:84%
Everybody who wants
to be a superstar.

01:24:19.677 --> 01:24:20.260 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Right.

01:24:20.260 --> 01:24:20.880 align:middle line:90%
The unlike.

01:24:20.880 --> 01:24:22.546 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: And they're
not like you at all.

01:24:22.546 --> 01:24:23.330 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Right.

01:24:23.330 --> 01:24:24.470 align:middle line:90%
That's interesting.

01:24:24.470 --> 01:24:26.860 align:middle line:84%
So if you really
do want to attract

01:24:26.860 --> 01:24:29.656 align:middle line:84%
the right type of
environment for yourself,

01:24:29.656 --> 01:24:30.780 align:middle line:90%
what would you have to say?

01:24:30.780 --> 01:24:32.725 align:middle line:90%
Be unlike that environment.

01:24:32.725 --> 01:24:35.850 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: Don't think of it
as attracting, as seducing.

01:24:35.850 --> 01:24:37.060 align:middle line:90%


01:24:37.060 --> 01:24:38.220 align:middle line:90%
It's not an attraction.

01:24:38.220 --> 01:24:39.870 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: You think
of it as being.

01:24:39.870 --> 01:24:40.370 align:middle line:90%
>>WOLF: No.

01:24:40.370 --> 01:24:41.340 align:middle line:90%
Think it as a giving.

01:24:41.340 --> 01:24:43.020 align:middle line:90%


01:24:43.020 --> 01:24:47.350 align:middle line:84%
You give to get in
this kind of thing.

01:24:47.350 --> 01:24:48.800 align:middle line:90%
So it's sharing.

01:24:48.800 --> 01:24:49.560 align:middle line:90%
It's giving.

01:24:49.560 --> 01:24:55.840 align:middle line:84%
It's providing a field in
which an invitation is offered

01:24:55.840 --> 01:25:00.150 align:middle line:84%
rather than a field in
which you say I want.

01:25:00.150 --> 01:25:00.820 align:middle line:90%
I want.

01:25:00.820 --> 01:25:01.600 align:middle line:90%
I want.

01:25:01.600 --> 01:25:05.260 align:middle line:84%
You get rid of one thing,
"I," and suddenly it

01:25:05.260 --> 01:25:08.400 align:middle line:84%
becomes the wanting,
and the wanting

01:25:08.400 --> 01:25:12.380 align:middle line:84%
is the field of wanting, and
everybody shares in that field.

01:25:12.380 --> 01:25:14.600 align:middle line:84%
So now learn to
identify with that

01:25:14.600 --> 01:25:16.860 align:middle line:84%
and then you can see
what is it that I

01:25:16.860 --> 01:25:18.680 align:middle line:84%
can give to that
field of wanting.

01:25:18.680 --> 01:25:21.380 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: That is what the
quantum field is all about.

01:25:21.380 --> 01:25:23.546 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: That is what the
quantum field is all about.

01:25:23.546 --> 01:25:26.700 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So in these experiments
where enough people intention

01:25:26.700 --> 01:25:30.460 align:middle line:84%
or meditate on one specific
outcome, that field,

01:25:30.460 --> 01:25:33.490 align:middle line:84%
that quantum field of wanting
without attachment or an ego

01:25:33.490 --> 01:25:36.160 align:middle line:84%
in specific ways of
having it turn out,

01:25:36.160 --> 01:25:37.660 align:middle line:90%
but that actually can work.

01:25:37.660 --> 01:25:40.230 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: It will work,
but the magical thing

01:25:40.230 --> 01:25:41.550 align:middle line:90%
is to give up the ego.

01:25:41.550 --> 01:25:45.760 align:middle line:84%
I mean, the point
is you-- you can't

01:25:45.760 --> 01:25:47.555 align:middle line:90%
be wanting it for yourself.

01:25:47.555 --> 01:25:49.200 align:middle line:90%


01:25:49.200 --> 01:25:53.120 align:middle line:84%
It doesn't quite-- the richest
people in the universe,

01:25:53.120 --> 01:25:55.050 align:middle line:84%
in the world, are
not people that

01:25:55.050 --> 01:25:57.510 align:middle line:90%
have made money for themselves.

01:25:57.510 --> 01:25:58.490 align:middle line:90%
There are exceptions.

01:25:58.490 --> 01:26:01.100 align:middle line:84%
I'm not going to say that,
but usually the exceptions

01:26:01.100 --> 01:26:02.770 align:middle line:84%
are the ones that
get thrown into jail.

01:26:02.770 --> 01:26:03.500 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

01:26:03.500 --> 01:26:04.833 align:middle line:90%
>>WOLF: Like the Ponzi schemers.

01:26:04.833 --> 01:26:06.190 align:middle line:90%


01:26:06.190 --> 01:26:10.080 align:middle line:84%
The people that are capable
of creating wealth for others

01:26:10.080 --> 01:26:11.485 align:middle line:90%
get very wealthy themselves.

01:26:11.485 --> 01:26:12.384 align:middle line:90%


01:26:12.384 --> 01:26:13.675 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Isn't that interesting?

01:26:13.675 --> 01:26:17.135 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: The people that are--
I mean, take Oprah Winfrey,

01:26:17.135 --> 01:26:17.635 align:middle line:90%
for example.

01:26:17.635 --> 01:26:20.510 align:middle line:84%
I mean, here's a
very remarkable woman

01:26:20.510 --> 01:26:25.340 align:middle line:84%
who has created an enormous
field for others to benefit

01:26:25.340 --> 01:26:28.480 align:middle line:84%
from her story, and
she's become one

01:26:28.480 --> 01:26:30.450 align:middle line:84%
of the richest
people in the world.

01:26:30.450 --> 01:26:33.682 align:middle line:84%
And not because she
wants to make money.

01:26:33.682 --> 01:26:35.140 align:middle line:84%
I never got her as
a money grabber.

01:26:35.140 --> 01:26:36.023 align:middle line:90%
That isn't her thing.

01:26:36.023 --> 01:26:37.340 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: She's rich in
spirit and rich in kindness.

01:26:37.340 --> 01:26:39.100 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: Because
she's spiritually

01:26:39.100 --> 01:26:41.940 align:middle line:84%
interested in
helping other people.

01:26:41.940 --> 01:26:44.425 align:middle line:84%
In fact, all of her shows are
based upon helping others.

01:26:44.425 --> 01:26:45.170 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

01:26:45.170 --> 01:26:46.260 align:middle line:90%
Absolutely.

01:26:46.260 --> 01:26:48.655 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: --and showing
how this can be achieved.

01:26:48.655 --> 01:26:50.210 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Absolutely.

01:26:50.210 --> 01:26:52.250 align:middle line:84%
That's exactly what this
show is about as well.

01:26:52.250 --> 01:26:55.790 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: And so that's what
we all have to be doing.

01:26:55.790 --> 01:27:00.710 align:middle line:84%
We have to be remembering
that we're not--

01:27:00.710 --> 01:27:02.335 align:middle line:90%
the self is an illusion.

01:27:02.335 --> 01:27:05.130 align:middle line:90%


01:27:05.130 --> 01:27:05.730 align:middle line:90%
It's illusion.

01:27:05.730 --> 01:27:09.490 align:middle line:84%
It's based upon survival of
the material substance, which

01:27:09.490 --> 01:27:12.250 align:middle line:84%
are the body interacting
with-- the mind interacting

01:27:12.250 --> 01:27:13.120 align:middle line:90%
with the body.

01:27:13.120 --> 01:27:16.900 align:middle line:84%
And if you identify with
that, then everything you do

01:27:16.900 --> 01:27:21.046 align:middle line:84%
will be to ensure the survival
at the cost of others.

01:27:21.046 --> 01:27:22.920 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So if you think
that you're stressed,

01:27:22.920 --> 01:27:26.262 align:middle line:84%
then that will become a reality
and it will form in other ways

01:27:26.262 --> 01:27:26.970 align:middle line:90%
around your life.

01:27:26.970 --> 01:27:28.720 align:middle line:84%
If you think the outcome
is going to be negative,

01:27:28.720 --> 01:27:30.674 align:middle line:84%
then that will form
around the rest of it.

01:27:30.674 --> 01:27:32.090 align:middle line:84%
So if it's all
really an illusion,

01:27:32.090 --> 01:27:34.520 align:middle line:84%
and if stress is an
illusion, and if negativity

01:27:34.520 --> 01:27:37.440 align:middle line:84%
is an illusion, then we
can turn that around.

01:27:37.440 --> 01:27:37.940 align:middle line:90%
Right?

01:27:37.940 --> 01:27:42.135 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: Negativity, stress
arise from one single word.

01:27:42.135 --> 01:27:43.070 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Survival.

01:27:43.070 --> 01:27:44.560 align:middle line:90%
>>WOLF: No.

01:27:44.560 --> 01:27:46.410 align:middle line:90%
I.

01:27:46.410 --> 01:27:47.250 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Interesting.

01:27:47.250 --> 01:27:51.610 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: If you think about
every negative thought you have,

01:27:51.610 --> 01:27:54.860 align:middle line:84%
I'm willing to bet
you dollars to donuts

01:27:54.860 --> 01:27:56.915 align:middle line:84%
that there is an I
in there somewhere.

01:27:56.915 --> 01:27:58.230 align:middle line:90%


01:27:58.230 --> 01:27:59.260 align:middle line:90%
Why did this happen?

01:27:59.260 --> 01:28:00.635 align:middle line:90%
Why did this happen to me?

01:28:00.635 --> 01:28:02.840 align:middle line:90%


01:28:02.840 --> 01:28:05.630 align:middle line:90%
Why am I this way?

01:28:05.630 --> 01:28:08.620 align:middle line:84%
Why can't I be like
her or like him?

01:28:08.620 --> 01:28:10.180 align:middle line:90%
Why am I so dumb?

01:28:10.180 --> 01:28:12.240 align:middle line:90%
Why can't I be smart like he is?

01:28:12.240 --> 01:28:13.400 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: So it's all---

01:28:13.400 --> 01:28:15.810 align:middle line:90%
>>WOLF: I. I. I. I. I. I. I.

01:28:15.810 --> 01:28:17.390 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So getting
off of yourself

01:28:17.390 --> 01:28:20.360 align:middle line:84%
and understanding that we're
part of this quantum field.

01:28:20.360 --> 01:28:22.350 align:middle line:84%
So what we've also
learned today,

01:28:22.350 --> 01:28:24.390 align:middle line:84%
and I thank you so much
for these perspectives

01:28:24.390 --> 01:28:27.410 align:middle line:84%
because it's-- in understanding
the quantum level of this,

01:28:27.410 --> 01:28:30.401 align:middle line:84%
it helps us understand
the macro level of it.

01:28:30.401 --> 01:28:30.900 align:middle line:90%
>>WOLF: Yes.

01:28:30.900 --> 01:28:32.900 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So we have
learned today a lot.

01:28:32.900 --> 01:28:36.260 align:middle line:84%
We've learned that it
is all an illusion.

01:28:36.260 --> 01:28:40.220 align:middle line:84%
We've learned that time itself
is based on the observer.

01:28:40.220 --> 01:28:43.370 align:middle line:84%
We've learned that we are the
creators of our own experiences

01:28:43.370 --> 01:28:46.585 align:middle line:84%
as long as it doesn't
involve the ego and the I.

01:28:46.585 --> 01:28:49.990 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: Well, it has to involve
the ego and I to some extent--

01:28:49.990 --> 01:28:50.991 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: To some degree.

01:28:50.991 --> 01:28:51.490 align:middle line:90%
Right.

01:28:51.490 --> 01:28:54.050 align:middle line:84%
>>WOLF: --because you're
here in a bodily form.

01:28:54.050 --> 01:28:58.440 align:middle line:84%
The whole thing is don't
identify with the ego I.

01:28:58.440 --> 01:29:01.160 align:middle line:90%
Experience it, yes.

01:29:01.160 --> 01:29:02.510 align:middle line:90%
You're hungry, eat.

01:29:02.510 --> 01:29:03.510 align:middle line:90%
You're tired, sleep.

01:29:03.510 --> 01:29:05.240 align:middle line:90%


01:29:05.240 --> 01:29:08.160 align:middle line:84%
You're in need of
love, reach out.

01:29:08.160 --> 01:29:11.060 align:middle line:84%
It doesn't mean that
you give it up all.

01:29:11.060 --> 01:29:14.680 align:middle line:84%
You don't lose it all,
but give it its relevance,

01:29:14.680 --> 01:29:17.370 align:middle line:84%
but don't make it
the only thing that's

01:29:17.370 --> 01:29:20.150 align:middle line:84%
important to what
your life is about.

01:29:20.150 --> 01:29:22.800 align:middle line:84%
Because really,
your greatest joy

01:29:22.800 --> 01:29:26.810 align:middle line:84%
will come from
compassion, understanding,

01:29:26.810 --> 01:29:29.240 align:middle line:90%
giving of yourself to others.

01:29:29.240 --> 01:29:30.540 align:middle line:90%
It's just the way it works.

01:29:30.540 --> 01:29:32.630 align:middle line:90%
And you get reward from that.

01:29:32.630 --> 01:29:35.140 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: It's just the way
the quantum world works.

01:29:35.140 --> 01:29:36.890 align:middle line:84%
That's the way the
quantum universe works.

01:29:36.890 --> 01:29:37.760 align:middle line:90%
>>WOLF: That's the way it works.

01:29:37.760 --> 01:29:39.430 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: That's a
great way to wrap up.

01:29:39.430 --> 01:29:40.400 align:middle line:90%
Thank you so much.

01:29:40.400 --> 01:29:41.110 align:middle line:90%
>>WOLF: You're very welcome.

01:29:41.110 --> 01:29:42.220 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: You've gone
full circle here,

01:29:42.220 --> 01:29:43.344 align:middle line:90%
and I really appreciate it.

01:29:43.344 --> 01:29:44.820 align:middle line:90%
Thank you, Fred.

01:29:44.820 --> 01:29:46.810 align:middle line:84%
So basically what
I've learned today

01:29:46.810 --> 01:29:49.990 align:middle line:84%
is that time is really
up to the observer

01:29:49.990 --> 01:29:53.320 align:middle line:84%
and that there is a
do-it-yourself approach to time

01:29:53.320 --> 01:29:55.640 align:middle line:84%
travel as Fred Alan
Wolf talked about.

01:29:55.640 --> 01:29:58.480 align:middle line:84%
But really, we are the creators
of our own experience--

01:29:58.480 --> 01:30:01.620 align:middle line:84%
our past, our present,
and our future--

01:30:01.620 --> 01:30:05.460 align:middle line:84%
and that this concept can really
apply to all areas of our life.

01:30:05.460 --> 01:30:06.300 align:middle line:90%
Thank you so much.

01:30:06.300 --> 01:30:09.900 align:middle line:84%
This is Lisa Garr, and
thanks for watching Gaiam TV.

